Murray Name Popularity

At NamesLook, the name Murray is recorded 3,133 times globally, ranking it as the 14,532th most common name worldwide.

Murray is most prevalent in United Kingdom, with 1,160 occurrences, making it the 1,036th most popular name in the country.
